{"tid":1680192,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"中國遊戲廠商騰訊對於《部落衝突：皇室戰爭》開發商 Supercell 取得多數控制權","createTime":"2019-10-28T15:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T13:40:51.000Z","uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5cfa312552a252d3458963ad42cace5ba4d1c0d0","tid":1680192,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:57:39.000Z","msg":"根據 gamesindustry 的外電報導指出，來自中國的遊戲巨擘騰訊在將債券轉換後，對於《部落衝突：皇室戰爭》開發商 Supercell 的可投票股份權益由 50% 增加至 51.2%，於實質上取得了多數控制權。而收購完成後，其財務業績、資產及負債將併入騰訊的財務報表。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W44dqm4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW44dqm4.jpg&h=92ba6f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，騰訊早在 9 月 25 日就已發布公告，表示公司將把對於 Supercell 的債券轉換為財團股份，並將原有的 50% 股份權益增持至 51.2%。而香港證交所也證實，騰訊已順利完成增持 Supercell 股權。<br />\n <br />\n  來自芬蘭赫爾辛基的遊戲公司 Supercell 曾推出像是《部落衝突》、《海島奇兵》、《部落衝突：皇室戰爭（Clash Royale）》以及《荒野亂鬥（Brawl Stars）》等膾炙人口的作品。"},{"pid":"69ee9d329f2d49e42bded93adbf1cf8fd51ef6f3","tid":1680192,"uid":94828,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:44:48.000Z","msg":"去apps台"},{"pid":"f5cc1f493f8aeec18d035beb062c90b6ba96533d","tid":1680192,"uid":51883,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:49:47.000Z","msg":"呢隻驚我到呢家都仲有玩"},{"pid":"a85f32da5ae67e3deee6e5f0c208a47a4c89a64d","tid":1680192,"uid":8021,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:48:09.000Z","msg":"Coc同Royale都有玩"},{"pid":"2c96b998502b857cb8168770e805a9ea09d4ce03","tid":1680192,"uid":214192,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:51:37.000Z","msg":"中共不斷侵蝕遊戲界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb664de423a0907781087aed0d5ba5784db05a8","tid":1680192,"uid":3212,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2c96b998502b857cb8168770e805a9ea09d4ce03","tid":1680192,"uid":214192,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:51:37.00